{"tid":1205225,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"極品上司用卑鄙手段 力阻員工6.12請假","createTime":"2019-06-11T17:34:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T23:48:10.000Z","uid":11585,"like":134,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"52a0d187c9838f96e59dd6a4e2557c8ad2915ed6","tid":1205225,"uid":11585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:34:39.000Z","msg":"今日我哋成team已經決定聽日罷工，然後老闆私下問我哋聽日點。咁我哋就如實作答，佢亦非常支持，仲叫我哋低調啲，話當我哋外出工作，email講返話補假就ok。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n隔咗一個鐘，阿姐突然一枝箭標過嚟問我哋聽日係咪唔返，我哋就話係。點知佢指住幾個未過試用期嘅同事，話佢哋幾個只可以請no pay sick leave，叫佢哋聽朝一定要去睇醫生，記得交返醫生紙喎。<br />\n<br />\n嘩！我聽到都呆咗，佢哋未過試用期，點都係no pay。就算請事假都唔使同你交代因由喇下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果嗰幾位同事再email多佢一次，話聽日想請一日事假，阿姐睇完即刻過嚟同佢哋講：「你哋未過試用期，只得1個選擇，就係no pay sick leave。事假係要有家人死咗先可以請，仲要係直系親屬先得，要有死亡證證明，唔係隨便請！」<br />\n<br />\n聽到呢到真係嬲到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />即刻走去問老闆條𡃁，佢話阿姐無權唔畀同事放no pay事假，而且老闆亦一早批准咗大家聽日唔開工。<br />\n<br />\n經過一輪交涉，最後阿姐成隻死狗咁過嚟話可以畀佢哋放no pay。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52c35d8237ce8bfcf79ee94c4f2cf28e811618f7","tid":1205225,"uid":32721,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T17:38:40.000Z","msg":"有個理智老細真係好緊要"},{"pid":"5a1d196389dffab048aa58eec632a1c022b2f427","tid":1205225,"uid":42767,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:37:33.000Z","msg":"香港地好多呢啲渣住雞毛當令箭嘅阿姐, 個老細都未壓榨啲撚樣就壓先, 好似有股份咁款"},{"pid":"61c216cc069804181d2b605e2d10faa7ca5cb10f","tid":1205225,"uid":63017,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T19:17:51.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">請廣傳</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望無論大家去邊，甚至返工，不了<br />\n都想大家連日常生活都黑衫黑褲口罩笠帽加黑鞋<br />\n令到平時條街見到全黑既人唔再係特徵反而係大多數<br />\n最好個個用現金，咁買飛個個就唔係做突出個一個<br />\n<br />\n全民 BLACK BLOCK<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1203119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1203119</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pQ2eUtV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpQ2eUtV.png&h=aefa5602&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"00424cf4c4390bb76e941e1a47adfe0e5ac1666f","tid":1205225,"uid":119347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a1d196389dffab048aa58eec632a1c022b2f427","tid":1205225,"uid":42767,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T18:37:33.000Z","msg":"香港地好多呢啲渣住雞毛當令箭嘅阿姐, 個老細都未壓榨啲撚樣就壓先, 好似有股份咁款"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:30:17.000Z","msg":"典型太監"},{"pid":"2516d86fed6bb6af9abd4067d4450da93596f000","tid":1205225,"uid":213142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:34:55.000Z","msg":"聖旨都敢抗，佢係咪老細情婦"},{"pid":"bc5067e5989052963f861028aaa16e0c6001096e","tid":1205225,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T22:36:42.000Z","msg":"屌 間公司佢有份咩<br />\n莊閒不分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ccd3805999cbafb3769c4c741fbabf948f3a0076","tid":1205225,"uid":28913,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:19:05.000Z","msg":"女人做上司真係害撚死人"},{"pid":"eb96e9fb3259bf402c62c1f1afa3b94bd0b862de","tid":1205225,"uid":26773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:23:29.000Z","msg":"事假係要有家人死咗先可以請，仲要係直系親屬先得，要有死亡證證明<br />\n<br />\n香港咪我地既家 死亡證明 今日十一點就有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ea70acd788e5f9ae9a0f80a81efc6714ceae5c6","tid":1205225,"uid":35637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T23:24:54.000Z","msg":"太監急<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p